<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=988585172765></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f988585172765><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=1&mid=988585172765>Looking for players to start a guild on Karana server</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Apr 29th 6:59 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>We are looking for people interested in starting a guild on Karana server.  We have about five players right now and we need ten or more, just to start the petitioning process for a guild charter.  This guild is being started up by primarily newbies (the highest leveled character being only level 13), but veterans are more than welcome to join.  It is open to all classes and races as well, so anyone can join.  For more information send a "tell" to Viego and tell him that Jotun sent you to join on this never ending quest...Viego will be the focal point for all guild proceedings.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
