n. I was attack by one and I barely survived. It can  immobilize you, poison, stun, and dizzy,which stops you from running and makes your sceen spin VERYVERYVERY fast.<br>Another note: Don't ask for anything. It will give you a reputation as a beggar and noone will waant to give you anything, maybe not even help if they're annoyed enough.                             Also, if you need it, some people may help you by buying food and drink for you inside Grobb(the Troll city-- Barbarians are KOS there due to race tensions.) when you need it if you provide the money or a little extra.<br><br>     An anonymous Troll Warrior of Xev server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
